Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Sanji who had parted ways\Nfinally reunited at the rendezvous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash Big Mom's tea party\Nand the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and save Sanji's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sanji'll be back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B... Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... She's the Emperor of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, Jimbei suggested a plan to Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Capone "Gang" Bege, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's the one who took Sanji away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main event of the tea party is\Nthe wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know, Big Mom intends to\Nkill all the members of the Vinsmokes at the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and acquire all of Germa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege is going to kill Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NSeems like everyone has their own plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Pekoms\Nbut under the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}do you really want to\Nmake an enemy of Bege?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Secret Meeting!\NLuffy vs. the Fire Tank Pirates!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you crazy, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually like it, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, four out of six of us are against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear about Bege-{\i1}san{\i0}'s ill deeds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that way, everything'll \Nwork out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make a decision like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, I've already made an arrangement.\NDo you want to meet him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's see him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NYou can say no if it feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is slightly different from theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy, Sanji. Bege and his clan's base is\Nin the northwest of the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The eight of us will head there first\Nfrom this dimension. See you there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop counting us in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
