Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Bobbin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he was going after Black-Leg.
