Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei isn't the type of man to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're both standing against Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we shouldn't make extra enemies -\Nhe's right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it depends on what Straw Hat will say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just kill him!
