Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:22.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,EASTERN INLET
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Pekoms! You still have to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! Has Jimbei really told Mama\Nabout that damn rat Bege?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By now, I'm guessing that the traitor Bege\Nhas been beaten relentlessly by Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! You guess?! Your guess isn't enough!\NI gotta make sure to tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to keep resting, Pekoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Praline,\Nin case they stop him from telling her... Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your concern,\Nit's even better for you to leave it to Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be beaten again in your condition now.\NJust keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Pekoms!\NAs a ship's doctor, I won't allow you to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--Rest! Rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something going on\Nall through the night in the inlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw some people carrying things around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't let Pekoms know that\NJimbei is trying to be part of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the Big Mom assassination plot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that you saved me\Nbut I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, we can't allow that!
