Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GULP!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE TANK PIRATES' BASE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Bege's base!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what Jimbei said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of him as a scheming\Nand brutal mafia boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hero! Vinsmoke Sanji of Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you again-{\i1}rero{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's everyone else?\NAre you Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush.\NThey are here or {\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "{\i1}rero{\i0}"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me worried, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for that... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside,\Nwhy do you look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys go take a bath too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you relaxing?! We don't have time!\NAnd you don't even like to bathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you two must take one too-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we'll talk-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bath under these circumstances?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father doesn't see anyone who is dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's dirty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NLola was turned into a warthog zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was chasing around\Nthe guy who she fell in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time and again\Nin the forest of monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what would've happened to me\Nif it weren't for Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! But you guys saved my sister too!\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm crying tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been very close since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A zombie! I can't imagine a dead person moving.\NThe sea is like a wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Lola has turned back to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure she's still \Ndoing well as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she found someone to marry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom sounded so mad when she talked about\NLola running away from a marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... that was a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama is reviled by all Giants \Nin the world for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Giants in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why even though\NTotto Land has a diverse population,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are no Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Giants really exist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man showed up saying he \Nhad fallen in love with Lola
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at first sight and wanted to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, believe it or not, he was\NLoki the prince of Elbaph, the Giants' country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A prince?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama became so happy and teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thought if Lola became \Nthe princess of Elbaph,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her long-standing feud with \Nthe Giants would be resolved
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she'd even get access to their army\Nwhich is said to be the world's strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, everything went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to use me as a substitute,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he noticed that I wasn't Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her relationship with the Giants\Ngot even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she gave up the idea of\Nbecoming friendly with actual Giants
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and started investing in research\Nto turn people into giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her anger towards Lola only amplified\Nand she was branded a criminal in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she comes back, she'll get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, she couldn't stand looking at me\Nbecause I look exactly like Lola...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get that damn face out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I saw her, she hit me without mercy.\NSo, for years, I always had fresh wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be killed by my own mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:16:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see that monster \Nas my mother anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since Lola is a happy-go-lucky girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she'd never imagine\Nthat her mother wants to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Everything makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when Bege said he was going to kill Mama,\NI felt nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might think I'm terrible\Nbut that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, the bath felt so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just like heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I refuse to move on to the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like we finished fighting.\NI can't get loose. We still have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}, Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found milk in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't go into our fridge without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I needed.\NMy tooth has cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my face broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.\NHave you really washed yourselves-{\i1}rero{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, totally!\NLet us see Bege already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we wear these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking great, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do {\i1}I{\i0} look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look nice too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look what I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the robot from Germa's comic strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they have that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, there's a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you come back with us,\NI'll drive you like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you'll never let me go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}extremely{\i0} sexy after a bath too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you, Chiffon?!\NI can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you help someone\Nwho wants to kill Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiffon-{\i1}sama{\i0}, please think twice!\NYou know no one can ever kill Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Brulee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what she has done to me, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lola is in danger\Nand Bege and Pez are my only family!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, which one of you is Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wait. He'll be here soon-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a bit cleaner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said "Clothes make the man."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do business with anyone\Nwho doesn't care about their appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have three and a half hours to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, whether or not we join forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Minister is here! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:09.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE OVEN\NMINISTER OF BAKING (FOURTH SON OF CHARLOTTE)\NBIG MOM PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:16.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BIG MOM'S TEA PARTY STARTS\NIN THREE AND A HALF HOURS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom's tea party starts\Nin three and a half hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy vs. Bege!\NThe chaotic meeting finally starts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one weak point for them\Nto take down the invincible Big Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is the secret weapon that holds the key\Nto fulfill the mission?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An unprecedented pirate alliance is formed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Deadly Pact! Luffy & Bege's Allied Forces!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:52.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
